quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Meem"
  2,2,"This is the Book. In it is guidance, sure, without doubt, for all who are mindful"
  2,3,"Who believe in the unseen, are steadfast in prayer, and give from what We have given them"
  2,4,"And who believe in the revelation sent to you, and sent before your time, and those who have an assurance of the hereafter"
  2,5,"They are guided by their Lord, and it is these who will flourish"